name: Productwidgetdemo
tagline: It is Spring Boot Project for Code Challege
body:
### Welcome to Product Widget Demo.
It is a demo project that implemented by Spring Boot, AngularJS, HTML, CSS, and Twitter BootStrap.
It contains both Backend (Restfull Web Service) and Front-End (Single Page Application).

### Backend
1. Spring Boot
2. Load Data from CSV files
3. Support GET and POST HTTP
4. Support JSON

### Front-End
1. Report - display highest, lowest, and average of products for each employee
2. Products - display and add New Product
3. Hours - display and add New Hour
4. Employees - display and add New Employee
